Launch the trainer first, then launch the Game and then Press F1 at the Main Menu.

Follow carefully! From the main menu, go to 'MY FIFA 12' then 'SETTINGS' then 'GAME SETTINGS'. Make sure the selection/highlight is over 'Half Length'. Activate this option. Use the arrow keys/controller to change this setting. Disable this option and exit this screen (ESC), WITHOUT moving any sliders! Now play a match and you should see that time passes very quickly now (each half will be about 1 minute each). You may need to save and then load or restart the game for this to take effect. To undo, simply re-enter the above menus and change the half length setting with the trainer option off.

In 'MANAGER MODE', make sure you are at the main screen (with the display of 'NEXT MATCH' etc), then choose 'TRANSFERS'. Activate this option. Now choose 'SCOUTING'. Once this screen has loaded, press ESC to return back to the main menu. Disable the option. You should now have more cash. Repeat if necessary, although be warned, the cash will increase in exponential amounts each time.

Follow carefully! From the main menu, choose 'VIRTUAL PRO'. Now either edit an existing pro or create a new one. Move to the 'PHYSICAL' stats screen (step 3), and make sure that the 'HEIGHT' field is selected/highlighted. Activate this option. Use the arrow keys to change your characters height. You should see all of the physical stats below max out. Once this has happened, disable the option and press ESC to move off this screen (be careful not to move any sliders after turning off the cheat else it will reset the stats). Note, this only changes a characters physical stats and not their other attributes such as ball control etc.
